eeded spot.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 615, \"end\": 630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Garcia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caroline Garcia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Garcia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Garcia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daria Saville has been called up as an alternate to replace Garcia, who was originally drawn against Qinwen Zheng.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria_Saville\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daria Saville\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria_Saville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria_Saville\"}, {\"begin\": 720, \"end\": 726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garcia\", \"score\": 0.999998565787001, \"rank\": 1.434214837090334e-06, \"text\": \"Garcia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garcia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garcia\"}, {\"begin\": 768, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3220209845663844e-32, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to spe