ian Wells and the Italian Open as well as the Eastbourne International in the run-up toWimbledon.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\", \"score\": 0.9999776145254982, \"rank\": 2.1714824864128267e-05, \"text\": \"Kazakh\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\"}, {\"begin\": 1549, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis\", \"score\": 0.9999999999076863, \"rank\": 9.214810875127385e-11, \"text\": \"tennis\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis\"}, {\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Wells_Masters\", \"score\": 0.9993708733516937, \"rank\": 0.0006287512080254945, \"text\": \"Indian Wells\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Wells_Masters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Wells_Masters\"}, {\"begin\": 1811, \"end\": 1835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastbourne_International\", \"score\": 0.9999999999149622, \"rank\": 8.060299107366541e-11, \"text\": \"Eastbourne International\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastbourne_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastbourne_International\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She opened up on her recent health issues during her SW19 campaign, saying: \\\"It's not easy because sometimes you have more energy and you want to do some interesting stuff.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 2036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes you are too tired and you just want to be on the couch after the matches.\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Carlos Alcaraz left in no doubt over Rafael Nadal a